f 2001 and Homeland Security Presidential Directives, potential national-level adverse impacts. Security categorization processes carried out by organizations facilitate the development of inventories of information assets, and along with CM-8, mappings to specific information system components where information is processed, stored, or transmitted.</li></ul><ul><li>#cm-8, related</li><li>#mp-4, related</li><li>#ra-3, related</li><li>#sc-7, related</li></ul></ul>",
